OL,3,CConstruction restarts on Jersey Zoo's
OL,4,Cnew gorilla house
OL,6,FConstruction on a new, larger gorilla
OL,7,Fhouse at Jersey Zoo is underway.
OL,9,FIt is the second phase of work on the
OL,10,Fproject to house the zoo's four
OL,11,Fgorillas, following a halt in work due
OL,12,Fto increasing material costs.
OL,14,FThe new enclosure will feature a
OL,15,Fmodern heating and cooling system,
OL,16,Feight separate bedroom spaces, as well
OL,17,Fas training and weighing areas.
