OL,3,CConstruction restarts on Jersey Zoo's
OL,4,Cnew gorilla house
OL,6,FThe Government of Jersey's planning
OL,7,Fcommittee approved plans for the new
OL,8,Fenclosure almost three years ago,
OL,9,Ffollowing a #980,000 grant to get
OL,10,Fconstruction underway.
OL,12,FIt is the biggest capital project the
OL,13,Fzoo has ever undertaken, with the sale
OL,14,Fof 40 gorilla sculptures also raising
OL,15,F#1,146,500 for the project in 2019.
OL,17,FThe zoo has said the new building will
OL,18,Fbring a lot of improvements, including
OL,19,Fresearch balconies and a full CCTV
OL,20,Fsystem to monitor the great apes'
OL,21,Fbehaviours.
