OL,3,CConstruction restarts on Jersey Zoo's
OL,4,Cnew gorilla house
OL,6,FCurator of Mammals, Ben Matthews,
OL,7,Fsaid: "The key features are a deep
OL,8,Fbark chip floor which will encourage
OL,9,Fnatural foraging behaviour and
OL,10,Fincrease the ambient humidity in the
OL,11,Fbuilding.
OL,13,F"It's much taller, so we've got a new
OL,14,Fclimbing structure being built inside
OL,15,Fwith over 50 points at the top of the
OL,16,Fstructure to attach ropes and webbing.
