OL,3,CConstruction restarts on Jersey Zoo's
OL,4,Cnew gorilla house
OL,6,F"The key message is progress and we're
OL,7,Ftaking all the good stuff we've learnt
OL,8,Fand not just at Jersey but in the
OL,9,Fwider zoo community and putting that
OL,10,Finto practice for what will be a very
OL,11,Fexciting build."
OL,13,FThe new enclosure should be completed
OL,14,Fin the summer of 2025.
